    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Well-kept good-condition car that shows nicely and has clearly been cared for over time. Paint, interior, and overall presentation are solid, with the expected light cosmetic wear and minor blemishes you\u2019d expect from a used vehicle rather than a showpiece. It feels like an honest, maintained example that should make a strong driver for someone who wants something presentable and usable without paying mint-condition money.",
