    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Clean, well-kept, and ready to enjoy, this is a strong example for someone who wants a nice driver without paying top-tier money. It presents very well overall, with the kind of honest wear you\u2019d expect from a good-condition car, and it still has plenty of appeal inside and out. A solid, attractive car that feels cared for and offers real value.",
      "price": 33900.0,
