      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Clean, honest good-condition example that presents well and should make a solid driver for its next owner. The body and paint show nicely overall, with the kind of normal age-related cosmetic wear you\u2019d expect on a well-kept car rather than a freshly restored showpiece. The interior appears tidy and usable, and the car gives the impression of having been maintained and enjoyed without being overpromised as perfect. A buyer should expect a presentable, enjoyable vehicle with some minor flaws consistent with age, but overall a strong, appealing example.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Opportunity-priced and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle is being offered as an affordable option for buyers seeking straightforward transportation or a worthwhile project. It shows clear signs of age and wear, but it still delivers solid value for someone who understands the appeal of a lower-cost entry point. A practical choice for the budget-minded shopper looking for honest value without the premium price tag.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels without spending a fortune? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid opportunity for someone who needs cheap transportation, a backup vehicle, or a project to tinker with. Priced fairly and described honestly, it offers a lot of value for the money if you know what you\u2019re looking at. If you want a straightforward deal from a seller who believes in being upfront, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Reliable budget-friendly driver/project with a strong-running engine, responsive automatic transmission, and a chassis that still feels composed on the road. Not a show car, but it has good bones and the kind of straightforward mechanical character that makes it easy to live with or improve over time. Ideal for someone who wants inexpensive transportation, a shop truck, or a solid starting point for a clean-up build. Priced to move and worth a look if you want practical value with usable everyday capability.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Rough around the edges, but gets the job done. Cheap entry point. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Honest, rugged, and full of old-school character, this car has the kind of presence that makes every drive feel a little more real. It\u2019s the sort of machine that\u2019s ready to be a dependable runabout, a budget commuter, or the perfect foundation for someone who enjoys bringing a classic daily back into its next chapter. There\u2019s charm here you just don\u2019t get from newer, cookie-cutter cars\u2014straightforward, practical, and packed with potential for the right buyer who appreciates substance over flash.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Straightforward and affordable, this vehicle offers an excellent opportunity for anyone seeking dependable basic transportation without a big upfront cost. It shows its age and is best suited for a value-minded driver, first-time buyer, or someone looking for a practical project. Priced to reflect its condition, it delivers real utility at a budget-friendly figure.",
      "price": 5995.0,
